pical project take?</h4><p>Timeline depends on scope, but most small business projects can be launched in a few weeks.</p><!-- /AI_SLOT:FAQ --><!-- AI_SLOT:CTA --><p><a class=\"button primary is-large\" href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/contact/\">Discuss Your Project</a></p><p>Related pages: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/website-service/\">Website Service</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/marketing-service/\">Marketing Service</a></p><!-- /AI_SLOT:CTA --><!-- AI_SLOT:SCHEMA --><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can you build something similar for my business type?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. We adapt layouts and messaging to your service category, market, and lead goals.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do you only do design, or full implementation too?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We handle both: planning, design, build, launch support, and ongoing optimization.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How long does a typical project take?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Timeline depends on scope, but most small business projects can be launched in a few weeks.\"}}]}</script><!-- /AI_SLOT:SCHEMA --></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n",
